### 3.5 Control Flow

#### Pattern Matching

Standard `switch` with exhaustiveness checking.

```typescript
function handle(msg: Message): number {
  switch (msg.tag) {
    case "Move": return msg.x + msg.y;
    case "Quit": return 0;
    case "Write": return msg.text.length;
  }
}
```

#### Loops

```typescript
// Iterator-based
for (const item of items) {
  console.log(item);
}

// Index loop
for (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {
  console.log(items[i]);
}

while (active) {
  // ...
}
```

